# RapidKit reconstructs generated module/runtime state from the committed
# project registry and locked dependencies after clone. Keep generated state
# out of the public examples repository.
**/.rapidkit/snapshots/
**/.rapidkit/audit/
**/.rapidkit/reports/
**/.rapidkit/tmp/
**/.rapidkit/vendor/

# Workspai runtime evidence is machine-local. Publish portable workspace
# foundations and contracts, but regenerate summaries/reports after cloning.
**/.workspai/reports/
**/.workspai/workspace-registry.v1.json
**/.workspai/imported-projects.json
**/.workspai/adopt.json
**/.workspai/adopt-readiness.json
